text: William Dennis Murphy (born October 24, 1944) is an American equestrian. He competed in the individual jumping event at the 1976 Summer Olympics. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1944 births Category:Living people Category:American male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of the United States Category:Equestrians at the 1976 Summer Olympics Category:Pan American Games medalists in equestrian Category:Pan American Games gold medalists for the United States Category:Equestrians at the 1975 Pan American Games Category:Sportspeople from Birmingham, Alabama
